    <div class="about-content">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <h3>Hi there!</h3>
        <p>Welcome to <b>DevDiaries</b> — a Learning Journey Tracking Platform created to help students and aspiring developers document their growth, stay consistent, and celebrate every milestone along the way.</p><br>
        <p>Learning to code is a journey filled with challenges, small victories, and continuous improvement. DevDiaries was built with the idea that recording what you learn each day not only reinforces your knowledge but also creates a valuable portfolio of your progress.</p><br>
        <p>Here, you can create rich-text learning entries, organize them with technology tags, save drafts, and publish them whenever you're ready. Beyond writing, DevDiaries helps you stay motivated with learning day tracking, progress timelines, streaks, goals, achievements, analytics, and personalized learning reports.<br> 
        <p>This isn't just a place to write blogs—it's a platform designed to help learners build consistency, reflect on their progress, and showcase their skills over time.</p><br>
        <p>Whether you're taking your first steps into programming or exploring new technologies, DevDiaries is here to encourage you to keep learning, one day at a time.</p>
        <p>Thank you for visiting, and we hope DevDiaries inspires you to document your journey, share your knowledge, and celebrate every milestone along the way.</p>
    </div>

